fields.description:
Description:
1.Run the sample code below on BB simulator/device
{code}
var win1 = Titanium.UI.createWindow({  
    backgroundColor:'#fff'
});
  
var lbl = Ti.UI.createLabel({
text:'Please select an item',
font:{fontSize:15},
height:'auto',
width:'auto',
color:'#000'
});
win1.add(lbl);
win1.open()
{code}
2.Notice the app after its is launched

Actual Result:
1.The label is not rendered if the height & width is set to 'auto'

Expected Result:
1.The label should be displayed

In the code I have used label you can verify it with any control
